Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-60,0:00:-03.-02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-03.00,0:00:00.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-16,0:00:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard the rumors about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got business with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Give back old diamond-head's gold!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:02:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean old man Cricket's stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I give anything back?\NI stole that stuff as a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a pirate yourself, you're in\Nno position to find fault with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're my friends. So I'm stealing it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"100 Million Man! World's Greatest\NPower and Pirate Blackbeard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to ask, but can you fight?!\NDo you know how to throw a punch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can a coward like you possibly do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No doubt about it! That's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you still got that?! Tear it\Nup and throw it away already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this wanted poster is real...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Bellamy stands a chance\Nagainst a 100 million-Berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! Just look at that runt!\NDoes he look nefarious to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me suspicious of his\N30 million bounty poster, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just stand there in\Nfear like this afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you ain't gonna steal\Nnothing from me, coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This afternoon was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That so? And just how is it different?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll shut your\Nsmart-alecky mouth for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Snipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Straw Hat flew, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amateur trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd that runt come all the way here for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all sit back and enjoy Bellamy's "show"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He talked all big, but now\Nhe's just running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's different at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna steal the gold back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a weakling who's all talk,\Nwho can't stand up to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and can't do anything but\Nblather on about dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:05:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's coming this way!\N--Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Struggle all you want--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no escape from my\NSpring-Spring Fruit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished already? Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that kid can stand\Na chance against Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't kill you, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to kick the bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.94,0:05:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My show's just getting to the good part!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did this when Roshio\Nthe Executioner was killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're your friends, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that geezer and\Nthose giant apes are just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a clan of natural-born\Nmorons who believe in a fish story
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,told by some guy 400 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A city of gold? A sky island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The era of dreams is over,\Nyou pathetic excuses for pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know how to throw a punch, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.45,0:06:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get 'im, Bellamy! That moron\Nisn't fit to live in reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Quit kiddin' around, Bellamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! You're just joking, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Bellamy! Quit acting dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, get up! Continue\Nyour usual show! Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a major rookie with a 55 million reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Those two from this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their bounties are higher than yours, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-See! I told you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old guy's gold. Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they're tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got all beat up,\Nbut now they're just fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.53,0:08:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know Chopper tended to 'em,\Nbut they almost seem immortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's, "Don't fight! Do this! Don't go! Go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I mean, they beat you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't really standing\Nin our way, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fights that leave nothing\Nbut sympathy are rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and get lost! You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what?! You're the one who never listens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why do I have to listen to you?!\N--Hey, now! Be careful there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys insane?! This ship\Nis our treasure! Hey! I said stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That runt... It was a fluke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I'm still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can lose\Nto dream-chasing morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Hey, Straw Hat!\NWhere're you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are the ones\Nwho defeated Sir Crocodile,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one of the Seven Warlords of the Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy... and Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Sword Style Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Thousand Worlds!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scars on the back are a swordsman's shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admirable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to surpass me! Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So those kids've grown to the point
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that they can shake up\Nthe World Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:55.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Holy Land of Marie Jois"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Red-Hair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:58.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He is acting disturbingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I assume he didn't take action himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He did so indirectly, using a messenger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too dangerous for Whitebeard\Nand Red-Hair to make contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:11.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"World Government Supreme Authorities\N'The Five Elder Stars'"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.28,0:11:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Red-Hair is formidable only when agitated;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he is not the type to change things\Nabout the world on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us be patient and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Seven Warlords of the Sea\Nare more important now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must find a successor for Crocodile quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not underestimate his loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The collapse of the Three Great Powers\Nwill fracture the world itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Balance must be maintained.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! That is why we have\Ncalled the Seven Warlords here,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.17,0:11:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but who knows how many will show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are pirates. They do as they please...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Crocodile. You've put\Nus in a dreadful situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.78,0:11:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can no longer let this man\Nwho beat you remain unchecked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy HQ to MaryJoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Quixote Doflamingo-sama\Nand Bartholomew Kuma-sama
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the Seven Warlords of the Sea have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.31,0:12:18.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Warlord of the Sea Don Quixote Doflamingo\NFormer Bounty: 340 Million Berries"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:25.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Warlord of the Sea Bartholomew Kuma\NFormer Bounty: 296 Million Berries"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! My hands are moving on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! This is no time for jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joking! I can't control my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell you can't...! I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you trying to kill me?!\N--It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Where you do think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:49.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy HQ Vice-Admiral\N'Great Tactician' Tsuru"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo! This is your doing! Stop it at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:13:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then start talking already,\Nor I'll end this lousy get-together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:07.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You idiot! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Make him stop, Doflamingo! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.20,0:13:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be fools! Did you\Ncome here to start a war?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:26.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy HQ Fleet Admiral\N(Naval Commander in Chief)\N'Saint Sengoku'"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon my late welcome.\NThank you for coming, scum of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Listen to the big-shot talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us begin. I doubt any more will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two out of six is better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't plan to come either, but my\Nisland's business is going so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I came out of sheer boredom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's disconcerting to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is as depressing to us\Nas a booming pirate industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite in-your-face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betray the "Saint" in your name,\NFleet Admiral Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear dreary bickering...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I perhaps come to the wrong place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawk-Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy HQ and the\NSeven Warlords of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That roundtable seems meaningless\Nfor those two opposing powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! A most unexpected man has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm simply an onlooker here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit interested in some pirates\Ninvolved with the issue at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I, too, am an onlooker...\NIs that acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:15:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose I'm not exactly an "onlooker"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?! How did you get in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what a truly eminent-looking\Ngroup you have here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come in the hopes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--...that I be allowed to join in your meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if at all possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do believe you have\Nstripped Crocodile of his title
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are now looking for a successor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.14,0:15:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...! Are you Lafitte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.17,0:15:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lafitte?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite honored!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a well-known\Npeace officer in West Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was chased from his country\Nfor being excessively violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who I am is of no importance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:16:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to recommend a certain man\Nfor the Seven Warlords of the Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks... That name brings back memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a letter from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It appears to be important,\Nso he gave it to me to deliver!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Well done, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm still new to the Red-Haired Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Red-Haired Pirates (Newcomer)\NRockstar\NBounty: 94 Million Berries"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I was a pirate before that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I think I made a bit of a name for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You guys've heard of Rockstar, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. Never heard of 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, the Sea King tasted great...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sending me a damn letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did that kid stoop\Nto being such a big-shot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He acted like this was an important letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Red-Hair you're dealing with!\NAre you sane in the head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain. That's probably\Nenough alcohol for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Something you drink when\Nyou wanna drink can't be bad for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My boss said this was an urgent letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a good idea what it's about.\NAce and Blackbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go tell that kid Red-Hair\Nthat if he wants to talk to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.06,0:17:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to come here himself,\Nand with some good booze, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go! I don't feel like talkin'\Nwith snot-nosed runts, you buffoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:55.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Strongest Man in the World 'Whitebeard'\NThe Great Pirate Edward Newgate"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man hasn't changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I had an inkling this'd happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a little more time! I've never\Nbeen insulted like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! What're you\Nplanning to do? Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help.\NYou can come straight back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, I have my pride...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is more important than your pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can do now.\NSorry for all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're you gonna do, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going. Prepare to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To see Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the government\Nwill keep quiet if you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government probably won't stay quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if they're gonna get in our way,\Nwe won't stay quiet, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:19:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men! It's battle time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Get some top-quality alcohol ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The captain of our pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of him.\NSome random, unknown guy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.53,0:19:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be no threat to other pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To that end, we are carefully devising a plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I ask for a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting! C'mon! Let 'em try, Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the Blackbeard Pirates.\NPlease remember that name...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear?! Bellamy was beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! By who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of ambitious spirit, I didn't\Nthink he was even worth 30 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think it was this high...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the plan, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.54,0:20:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't just stand there gawking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really ticked off right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut... up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got no business with small-fries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for a head\Nworth over 100 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to join the big leagues now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time to hunt some prey has finally come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Weren't we supposed to\Nmeet up with Lafitte in this town?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:46.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blackbeard Pirate Helmsman\N'The Champion'\NJesus Burgess"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems we got separated!\NBut that's how luck is sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Auger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:21:00.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blackbeard Pirate Captain\N'Blackbeard'\NMarshall D. Teach"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:04.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blackbeard Pirate Sniper\N'The Supersonic'\NVan Auger"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely! Destiny always\Nmeasures a person's worth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.97,0:21:17.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Blackbeard Pirate Doctor\N'The Reaper'\NDoc Q"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old diamond-head! I got your gold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I'll be there soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break! I'm scared here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.18,0:23:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being sucked into the whirlpool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody said anything about a\Ngiant whirlpool! This is a scam!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.56,0:23:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's turn back! The sky island\Nis just a dream within a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An island in a dream within a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.56,0:23:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll regret it for life if I pass\Nup such a big adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take to the Sky!\NRide the Knock-Up Stream"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
